cs.SD, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.SY, cs.AI

Reasoning: 
- cs.SD (Sound): The paper focuses on speech enhancement, which is related to sound processing. 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language): The paper deals with speech processing and language transfer, which are relevant to this category. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning): The paper uses deep learning techniques, specifically generative adversarial networks, for speech enhancement. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper discusses the adaptability of speech enhancement systems in new environments, which is related to system control. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper uses AI techniques for speech enhancement and transfer learning.
